### 1. Landing Page — what does this OGC server offer?
GET https://demo.pygeoapi.io/master/
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Conformance — what OGC standards does it support?
GET https://demo.pygeoapi.io/master/conformance
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. OGC API - Features: List all collections
GET https://demo.pygeoapi.io/master/collections
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. OGC API - Features: Get items from a specific collection
GET https://demo.pygeoapi.io/master/collections/lakes/items?limit=3
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. OGC API - Features: Filter by bounding box
GET https://demo.pygeoapi.io/master/collections/lakes/items?bbox=-180,-90,180,90&limit=5
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. OGC API - Records: Search the catalog
GET https://demo.pygeoapi.io/master/collections/dutch-metadata/items?limit=3
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. OGC API - Processes: List available processes
GET https://demo.pygeoapi.io/master/processes
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. OGC API - Processes: Get details of hello-world process
GET https://demo.pygeoapi.io/master/processes/hello-world
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. OGC API - Processes: EXECUTE a process (POST)
POST https://demo.pygeoapi.io/master/processes/hello-world/execution
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "inputs": {
        "name": "GSoC MCP Project",
        "message": "Hello from our MCP server!"
    }
}

